Two bodies entangled up tonight amongst themselves in a foggy parking lot
Hidden beneath the spot of illuminated lamp post

Electricity between them buzzes with each second
Sparking into another miniature minute

His fingers disappeared into the ... of her hair
And hands vibrating against the ... of his back

Their shared heat cools the air
As passion secretly instigates the slow dance
Into slow, ... rutials


